reviewText: Loved this video. It was as if I were in Switzerland. The Adair's are a wonderful couple who make the best travel destination videos I've ever seen. Hope there are more to come soon.

I FOUND THIS ARTICLE VERY INFORMATIVE, AND LOOK FORWARD TO ORDERING AND VIEWING THIS VIDEO.  I HAVE BEEN IN SWITZERLAND AND WANT TO TRAVEL NEXT TIME BY TRAIN AND GET-OFF AT INTERESTING LOCATIONS...WITH THE HELP FROM YOUR TRAVEL TID-BITS. THANKS.
